      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry what? goblin guardian?? i'm just trying to understand the legal stuff for my mortgage. can u just explain it normally without the metaphors please? who actually holds the money and how do i know they won't just disappear with it?",
      "source": "evaluator"
